### 设置 count
GET http://{{host}}/api/test/lock/set-count?value=1

### 减少 count，不加锁
GET http://{{host}}/api/test/lock/decrease-count
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/test/lock/decrease-count

### 减少 count，加锁
GET http://{{host}}/api/test/lock/decrease-count-with-lock
# ab.exe -n 10 -c 10 http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/test/lock/decrease-count-with-lock

#=======================================================================================================================

### Thread.Sleep
GET http://{{host}}/api/test/lock/thread-sleep

